text: ยง 13-126 Contributions of members and their use; annuity reserve fund. The annuity reserve fund shall be the fund from which shall be paid all annuities and all benefits in lieu of annuities, payable as provided in this chapter.

chapter.text: NEW YORK CITY EMPLOYEES' RETIREMENT SYSTEM
